# New Era Fight Night Arena

This project showcases modifications and event infrastructure added to a pre-existing arena on the New Era map.

The original arena structure was created by the New Era map developer, Noa. My contribution focused on adapting the space for community events hosted by Lonely Outcasts.

## Modifications

- Added decorative elements throughout the arena
- Added food and water sources for event participants
- Constructed a concrete perimeter fence around the entire arena
- Created a controlled choke-point entrance and exit
- Improved spectator and participant flow
- Adapted the area for organized Fight Night events

## Purpose

The goal of these modifications was to transform an existing arena into a functional event venue capable of supporting large community gatherings while improving organization, player movement, and event management.

## Skills Demonstrated

- Event planning
- Player flow design
- Arena modification
- Community event infrastructure
- Creator Mode construction
- Environmental detailing
